title: Feature: change plugin behavior:
message:
Feature: change plugin behavior:

1) the first time the app connects to gps, a dialog to select account will pop.
2) after login in with an account, that account will always connect until a manual call to disconnect is done.
3) after singing out, the same dialog as in step 1 will pop.

Also, you can control the behavior of auto login with sdkbox_config.json 'connect_on_start' parameter.
